This song has brought so much joy to the world during these difficult times we are currently living in 😩❤️ 

No matter how old you are, you can’t help but smile when it plays ☺️ It oozes positivity and has such a feel good vibe to it....really does hit you right in the feels 🥰😭

We had the pleasure of joining the students of our local school “Scoil Nuachabháil” before Christmas and lockdown to do a bitta Jerusalema 🤣

The staff & students were absolutely amazing !! ..... we need to keep the positive vibes flowing because by god we need it now more than ever ☺️

#FridayFeeling #JerusalemaChallenge #PositiveVibes #GardaJerusalema
